Class NetworkListener

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      controller.NetworkListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class NetworkListener
extends java.lang.Thread

NetworkListener is a thread attached to a GameFrameController He is charged to receive/send messages from BeginingMessage to the last message The information transmission is totally separated from the graphic part (the view is not blocked during data send/reception)
